\section{Conclusion}
The new Fair and Unbiased Assessment System seeks to promote a fair and effective assessment process in universities. Currently, universities use a variety of methods in assessing students. For example, in quizzes and assignments, a teacher may have to go through a lot of work in assessing the quizzes and assignments of students. It may take a lot of time and may also be prone to human error or bias.

The new assessment system will enable students to upload their assessment in PDF format. After uploading, an AI tool will analyze the assessment and determine the marks earned and mistakes made. The results will be stored in a MySQL database. It will also enable the creation of a performance report for students and teachers.

The new assessment system will help reduce the workload of a teacher and promote a fair assessment process. It will also provide a more effective and organized method of assessment.

